name: edgetest-pip-tools
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "edgetest-pip-tools" %}
{% set version = "2022.4.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: a05004cd6b623463b05e7012f40caa96aa5eece8ab9bc30c6575d4b935aa0150

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install -vv --no-deps .

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.7
    - pip
  run:
    - edgetest >=2021.12.3
    - pip-tools >=6.0.0,<=6.4.0
    - python >=3.7

test:
  imports:
    - edgetest_pip_tools.plugin

about:
  home: https://github.com/capitalone/edgetest-pip-tools
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: edgetest-pip-tools is a pip-tools plugin for edgetest
  description: |
    This plugin will refresh requirements.txt using pip-tools when using edgetest
  doc_url: https://capitalone.github.io/edgetest-pip-tools/
  dev_url: https://github.com/capitalone/edgetest-pip-tools

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - fdosani
    - ak-gupta
